    "Real-world validation ensures that the models align with ethical standards and demonstrate effectiveness in practical healthcare applications.",
    "Despite the promising results of the study, there are several limitations that need to be addressed in future research:",
    "Data quality and representation The dataset used in the study was limited to a specific population and may not be generalizable to other populations or clinical settings.",
